## Resource Monitor Configuration

{%- if account_strategy == 'Single Account' %}
{%- set prefix = data_product_domain | upper ~ '_' ~ data_product_name | upper ~ '_' ~ data_product_environment | upper %}
{%- elif account_strategy == 'Multi-Account (Environment-based)' %}
{%- set prefix = data_product_domain | upper ~ '_' ~ data_product_name | upper %}
{%- elif account_strategy == 'Multi-Account (Domain-based)' %}
{%- set prefix = data_product_name | upper ~ '_' ~ data_product_environment | upper %}
{%- elif account_strategy == 'Multi-Account (Domain + Environment)' %}
{%- set prefix = data_product_name | upper %}
{%- endif %}

### Monitor Details

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| **Name** | `{{ prefix }}_MONITOR` |
| **Credit Quota** | {{ resource_monitor_credits }} credits |
| **Frequency** | {{ resource_monitor_frequency }} |
| **Start Time** | Immediately |

### Notification Thresholds

| Level | Threshold | Action |
|-------|-----------|--------|
| Warning | 50% | Notify |
| Alert | 75% | Notify |
| Critical | 90% | Notify |
| Limit | 100% | Suspend |

### Credit Consumption Estimate

Based on configured warehouses:

| Warehouse | Size | Max Credits/Hour | Max Credits/{{ resource_monitor_frequency }} |
|-----------|------|------------------|---------------------------------------------|
{%- set period_hours = {'DAILY': 24, 'WEEKLY': 168, 'MONTHLY': 720, 'QUARTERLY': 2160, 'YEARLY': 8760} %}
{%- set hours = period_hours.get(resource_monitor_frequency | upper, 720) %}
{%- for wh in warehouse_configuration %}
{%- set credits_per_hour = {'X-SMALL': 1, 'SMALL': 2, 'MEDIUM': 4, 'LARGE': 8, 'X-LARGE': 16, '2X-LARGE': 32, '3X-LARGE': 64, '4X-LARGE': 128} %}
{%- set hourly = credits_per_hour.get(wh.size | upper, 1) * wh.max_cluster_count %}
| `{{ prefix }}_WH_{{ wh.name | upper }}` | {{ wh.size }} | {{ hourly }} | {{ hourly * hours }} |
{%- endfor %}

### Warehouses to Monitor

The resource monitor will be assigned to:
